      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SUNSET CALIGULA (7) is a talented type progressing through the grades and building a strong record. Has been on speed to score at his last couple of runs. Latest win recorded a handy 30.09 at this track. Form reads well for this. ZIPPING COLUMBUS (1) has been a little hard to follow, finishing out of the placings latest but was in winning form two back scoring in a Grade 5 at Sandown. Has the ability and can find best this time. FOOT FALCON (2) collided with another runner and was out of the placings when a 20 length eighth (31.06) in a Novice race at this track. Should be in this for a long way. ICONIC GUESS (3) won last start after racing on the pace. Sure to run well again.",
